nba_play_by_play.name: nba_play_by_play
nba_play_by_play.schema:
CREATE TABLE nba_play_by_play (-- data about the play by play events in NBA games
    action_number bigint, -- unique identifier for each action
    clock bigint, -- time remaining on the game clock in milliseconds
    time_actual timestamp with time zone, -- actual time the action occurred
    period bigint, -- period of the game
    x_legacy double precision, -- x coordinate of the action
    y_legacy double precision, -- y coordinate of the action
    is_field_goal bigint, -- whether the action is a field goal or not
    team_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the team
    jump_ball_recoverd_person_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the person who recovered the ball in a jump ball
    jump_ball_won_person_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the person who won the jump ball
    jump_ball_lost_person_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the person who lost the jump ball
    shot_distance double precision, -- distance of the shot
    points_total double precision, -- total points scored
    assist_person_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the person who assisted the shot
    assist_total double precision, -- total assists
    turnover_total double precision, -- total turnovers
    steal_person_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the person who stole the ball
    shot_action_number double precision, -- unique identifier for the shot action
    rebound_total double precision, -- total rebounds
    rebound_defensive_total double precision, -- total defensive rebounds
    rebound_offensive_total double precision, -- total offensive rebounds
    official_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the official
    foul_personal_total double precision, -- total personal fouls
    foul_technical_total double precision, -- total technical fouls
    foul_drawn_person_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the person who drew the foul
    block_person_id double precision, -- unique identifier for the person who blocked the shot
    person_id bigint, -- unique identifier for the person
    x double precision, -- x coordinate of the action
    y double precision, -- y coordinate of the action
    possession bigint, -- possession of the ball
    score_home bigint, -- score of the home team
    score_away bigint, -- score of the away team
    order_number bigint, -- order of the action
    period_type text, -- type of period
    action_type text, -- type of action
    sub_type text, -- subtype of action
    qualifiers text, -- additional qualifiers for the action
    value text, -- value of the action
    player_name text, -- name of the player
    player_name_i text, -- name of the player in international format
    jump_ball_won_player_name text, -- name of the player who won the jump ball
    block_player_name text, -- name of the player who blocked the shot
    jump_ball_lost_player_name text, -- name of the player who lost the jump ball
    edited text, -- whether the action was edited or not
    game_id text, -- unique identifier for the game
    steal_player_name text, -- name of the player who stole the ball
    shot_result text, -- result of the shot
    foul_drawn_player_name text, -- name of the player who drew the foul
    side text, -- side of the court
    description text, -- description of the action
    person_ids_filter text, -- filter for person ids
    assist_player_name_initial text, -- initial of the name of the player who assisted the shot
    team_tricode text, -- tricode of the team
    descriptor text, -- descriptor of the action
    jump_ball_recovered_name text -- name of the player who recovered the ball in a jump ball
);
